metadata.name: secretary, how did you two
metadata.description:
out of the car, quickly took out a box of cigarettes, to the two of them.



"Don't do that. What did you promise me last month? You RAISE THOSE cockroaches, earthworms, centipedes, scorpions and so on, I also don't say what, after all, those things count medicine, but how do you raise so many mice? You think you can raise this shit? What if the plague breaks out?"
